- Technical Details
    - Tech Stack:
        - Bash (no external dependencies)
        - JSON via line-by-line parsing (no jq required)
        - Standard git hooks
    - Key Files:
        - skill.sh: The CLI tool (all commands)
        - skills/: Skill source directories
        - manifest.json: Auto-generated skill metadata cache
        - groups.json: Hand-maintained group definitions
        - templates/SKILL.md: Template for new skills
        - tests/test_skill.sh: Test suite (44 tests)
    - Architecture Notes:
        - Single-file CLI with helper functions per command
        - Skills are self-describing via YAML frontmatter
        - 3-layer sync: generation, lazy validation, pre-commit hook
        - Source tracking via .skill-source marker files

